<h2 id="breadcrumbs-1">Breadcrumbs</h2>

<p>Breadcrumbs show users where they are in the website hierarchy and they provide a way to navigate through previous levels of content.</p>

<p>They should always be displayed at the top of the page.</p>

<p>We also remove hyperlink styles for the last-child in the breadcrumbs.</p>
